

🎮 When Was the Golden Era of Video Games?

📌 Project Overview

This project explores the golden era of video games by analyzing sales data alongside critic and user ratings. The goal is to identify:

* The best-selling games of all time
* The years with the highest critic acclaim
* The years where both critics and users agreed on game quality


📊 Dataset Summary

The analysis uses three key tables:

* `game_sales` → Game sales data
* `reviews` → Critic and user ratings
* `users_avg_year_rating` & `critics_avg_year_rating` → Precomputed yearly averages


